commit.title: - All DSSS2018 prerequisites built except for QuickChick
commit.message:
- All DSSS2018 prerequisites built except for QuickChick
- Reenabled log file logging for Coq build
- Added Coquelicot addon
- Created build_prep_overaly and used it for ci-overlay controlled components
- Fixed quickchick addon - mostly fixed ocamlfind for coq libs
- Added addon aactactics + fixed related unzip reliability issue + installer path issue
